{"tid":1894932,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"教協出post回應何栢欣老師事件 成班藍絲入哂黎","createTime":"2020-02-24T08:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T10:22:26.000Z","uid":12746,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52b7c1d680b00b0dc027d5b5ec2f3ebafdcaa046","tid":1894932,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T08:59:07.000Z","msg":"【教協就孔聖堂中學何栢欣老師事件的聲明】<br />\n新聞稿<br />\n2020年2月24日<br />\n教協就孔聖堂中學何栢欣老師事件的聲明<br />\n<br />\n教協關注孔聖堂中學就何栢欣老師於網上貼文一事所發表的聲明，校方表示已成立專責小組調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，何老師在其社交平台所發布的帖文，並非他原創。他在轉貼時，只是贊同字面表達的意思，認同應以同心為香港的態度面對現時的疫情，並無留意原來當中另有含意。當他知道文章內含有其他意思時，已即時刪除有關的社交平台，以免造成誤會。<br />\n<br />\n教協促請校方能如聲明中所指，查明事件的來龍去脈和真相，並以公平、公正、符合程序公義的原則處理整件事。視乎老師的需要，教協也會提供協助和法律支援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkptunion/photos/a.622869427788003/3503853866356197/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkptunion%2Fphotos%2Fa.622869427788003%2F3503853866356197%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpArTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=c513c5a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkptunion/photos/a.622869427788003/3503853866356197/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n成班藍絲入哂黎係到屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a75caf07ea0fdf40719af28ae2484b3bae6adc1","tid":1894932,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1509a2987bf0adb9631d8deea7012ed0060ccaa","tid":1894932,"uid":12746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"幫手洗下板 咪撚俾人搞串哂個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5be7f3974bd940d790ad71aba1c25d3137ceab","tid":1894932,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cc169dd1069855a146261da7c1339ee8418c71d","tid":1894932,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8416fe24d413170794382c1208e56549ece8a0e4","tid":1894932,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71c622b823d97a5d64ddaf5fba54511a9fb2908","tid":1894932,"uid":253479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:18:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5fcdb8b21518f9c382c38bdbe1766b55cbb3ba3","tid":1894932,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fb12f08c65a1ff1b57be8cfd4385647fea28d44","tid":1894932,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:20:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f9d6991dfd8077cf16dc3158df18cda7c8596eb","tid":1894932,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e78268939bb37855b2a579c6d9d541962e093d9","tid":1894932,"uid":154106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"推，本鍵盤戰士去幫手屌藍屍先"},{"pid":"1b6d5dab9574c3704829c8feeb1074e75793eb02","tid":1894932,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"唔睇comment"},{"pid":"1f5f8b3cb96e299a90c972319201798004b4a3d7","tid":1894932,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:51:01.000Z","msg":"趕走藍屍狗"},{"pid":"eb8c4b0b239f715b0a1f27d89c47b61e191ec76a","tid":1894932,"uid":12746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T09:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a508396ebcafbb73d7323a5e31d92488afd8d6b","tid":1894932,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply